Titolo: Shadow Warrior 2

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Shadow Warrior 2 is a first-person shooter game developed by Flying Wild Hog and published by Devolver Digital. It is the sequel to the 2013 Shadow Warrior, the reboot of the 1997 original. The game was released for Microsoft Windows in October 2016, for PlayStation 4 and Xbox One in May 2017, and Xbox Game Pass in December 2018. A sequel, Shadow Warrior 3, was revealed on July 6, 2020.